{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2dbc9cac72","title":"中央文革关于湖南红旗军、红导弹等红卫兵组织到湖南军区动手打人、抓人问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"460000db2f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"2dbc9cac72"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"94b82e4994","name":"中共中央决定、指示等","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"413eee3aba","type":"title","text":"中央文革关于湖南红旗军、红导弹等红卫兵组织到湖南军区动手打人、抓人问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72"},{"id":"2e6bf68927","type":"paragraph","text":"军队负有战备任务和保卫文化大革命任务。不能允许外人冲入指挥、保密等系统，不许接管。红旗军是反动组织，必要时将其少数头头逮捕，可起分化瓦解作用。军区负责人，应挺身而出，对群众进行说服教育工作。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72"},{"id":"a2e7926803","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央  国 务 院","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72"},{"id":"787426d80e","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委  中央文革","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72"},{"id":"4ca02aba6d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年一月二十日凌晨","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72"}],"page":{"id":"231e31df91","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"2dbc9cac72","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}